name: MisLead (Xemulator)
description:
MisLead is a little 2d platformer/jumper I create in a recent DevLog on my youtube channel "Xemulator". It is a little bit of a puzzle game as well as a platformer though where you need to jump onto different platforms around you until you eventually find the finish line.  There is also fake finish lines though so dont be mislead! You might spent 5 minutes jumping on platforms in one direction just to find that you have gone the wrong way. I believe it would be a great game to race against your friends in and speedrun. It will be getting updates most likely fixing small issues and making the map bigger and harder,  possibly adding more levels even.  Enjoy:) 

Controls:

The basic controls are

move left - A/right arrow 

move right - D/left arrow

jump - space bar

to press buttons use the left mouse button

those are all the controls but they are also in the game if you need them.
